<s> Subject: Re: QED &amp; Marshall McLuhan Date: Friday, June 11, 1999 11:38 AM After reading the past several days on this topic, it seems reasonably obvious to me that something is necessary for some segment of the population with cognitive disabilities who has the ability to access the web to understand what they are accessing.  </s>
