<s> You had to go to the 4th definition in order to find something that supports your equation of "accessibility" and "understandability" though.  </s>
<s> Note that the first one doesn't speak of understanding, just of ease of _access_.  </s>
<s> The second says _able_ to be used, not a guarantee of understanding.  </s>
<s> The third says "obtainable" which does _not_ imply understanding.  </s>
<s> Finally in the fourth definition, you hit yours; then you come to one that says web content must be bribable?  </s>
<s> If you want to play this dictionary game, we can, but are you really calling for web sites to be open to corruption?  </s>
<s> My definition: A web site is accessible if the information contained  </s>
<s> in the content is not denied to any user.  </s>
<s> This is separate from the actual _understanding_, meaning that a web site could be perfectly _accessible_ to me but not _understandable_ by me, and that's just fine.  </s>
